== Tr8n on Rails 3.0.8

To try it, run the following commands:

  $ git clone git://github.com/hatem/tr8n308.git
  $ cd tr8n308
  $ bundle
  $ rake db:create
  $ rake db:migrate
  $ rake tr8n:init
  $ rails s

